          "publishedOn": "2025-01-04T18:30:00.000Z",
          "wordCount": 1862,
          "title": "Saka 馬鹿",
          "imageUrl": "https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2023/02/08/15/10/sculpture-7776861_1280.jpg"
        },
        {
          "id": "https://www.manjusaka.blog/posts/2024/12/31/at-the-end-of-2024/",
          "author": null,
          "description": "<p>每年都会选择一句话来总结自己这一年，前年是“但行好事，莫问前程”，去年是 “Per aspera, Ad astra”。那么今年我选择是 “本当の僕らをありがとう”。</p>\n<p>这句出自 《Angel Beats!》的片尾曲《My Song》。含义为“向最真实的我们致谢”</p>",
          "link": "https://www.manjusaka.blog/posts/2024/12/31/at-the-end-of-2024/",
          "publishedOn": "2024-12-31T15:00:00.000Z",
          "wordCount": 1669,
          "title": "本当の僕らをありがとう",
          "imageUrl": "https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2023/02/04/07/38/cherry-blossoms-7766587_1280.jpg"
        }
      ]
